European Coal Falls to $127.50 a Metric Ton in London Trading

-- B y   A l i s t a i r   H o l l o w a y
-- 
2011-06-22T09:45:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/european-coal-falls-to-127-50-a-metric-ton-in-london-trading.html
European coal derivatives fell.  Coal for delivery to Amsterdam, Rotterdam or Antwerp with
settlement next year retreated 15 cents to $127.50 a metric ton
by 10:36 a.m. in  London .  The data are drawn from information supplied by ICAP Plc,
 GFI Group Inc. (GFIG) , Spectron Group Ltd., Credit Suisse Group AG, IHS
McCloskey, Bloomberg, Tradition Financial Services and Tullett
Prebon Plc.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alistair Holloway in London at 
